<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd" []>
<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="external-entity" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>External Entity</title>
  <conbody id="body">
    <p id="external-entity-intro">An <keyword>external entity</keyword> is saved to a separate file and can be reused in any document.<fig frame="all">
        <title>External entity in the Editing Window and ContentMap.</title>
        <image href="external-entity-in-the-editing-window-and-content-map.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
      </fig></p>
    <p>You can do the following operations with internal entities:<ul>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="converting-to-external-entity.xml">
              <b>Convert a part of document content to an external entity</b>
            </xref></p>
          <p conref="converting-to-external-entity.xml#converting-to-external-entity/convert-to-external-entity-intro"/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="inserting-external-entity.xml">
              <b>Insert an external entity</b>
            </xref></p>
          <p conref="inserting-external-entity.xml#inserting-external-entity/insert-external-entity-intro"/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="converting-from-external-entity.xml">
              <b>Convert an external entity to a regular content</b>
            </xref></p>
          <p conref="converting-from-external-entity.xml#converting-from-external-entity/convert-from-external-entity-intro"/>
        </li>
      </ul></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
